      "text": "Mode:  [Auto]  [Manual]   \u2014 setMode(\"auto\" | \"manual\")\nDays:  [7]  [14]  [21]  [30]  \u2014 setSimStepCount(n)        default: 14\nactionableSkillCap = getActionableSkillCap(simStepCount, nSkills)   \u2192 5/10/15/20 (days \u22647/14/21/30)",
