      "updated": 1703000000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Paths sliced to simStepCount:  toSimPath(bp) \u2192 trajectory.filter(p => p.step <= simStepCount)\n\nPath A  \u2500\u2500  #ef4444  Focused Retrieval Practice    (from sc.path_a)\nPath B  \u2500\u2500  #f59e0b  Spaced Repetition             (from sc.path_b)\nPath C  \u2500\u2500  #6366f1  Desirable Difficulty          (from sc.path_c)\nPath D  - -  #14b8a6  Custom Selection             (manual mode only \u2014 client-side ZPD preview)\n\nbestSimName: highest avgMastery at simStepCount across A/B/C\nhorizonFitLabel: for each path, DAY_OPTIONS windows where it leads by >0.05%\n  Short-term (\u226414d) | Long-term (\u226521d) | All horizons | Nd\u2013Md range",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Paths sliced to simStepCount:  toSimPath(bp) \u2192 trajectory.filter(p => p.step <= simStepCount)\n\nPath A  \u2500\u2500  #ef4444  Focused Retrieval Practice    (from sc.path_a)\nPath B  \u2500\u2500  #f59e0b  Spaced Repetition             (from sc.path_b)\nPath C  \u2500\u2500  #6366f1  Desirable Difficulty          (from sc.path_c)\nPath D  - -  #14b8a6  Custom Selection             (manual mode only \u2014 client-side ZPD preview)\n\nbestSimName: highest avgMastery at simStepCount across A/B/C\nhorizonFitLabel: for each path, DAY_OPTIONS windows where it leads by >0.05%\n  Short-term (\u226414d) | Long-term (\u226521d) | All horizons | Nd\u2013Md range",
      "lineHeight": 1.4
    },
