      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "isBest: effectiveBestName === path.name  (effectiveBestName = whatIfAdvice.best_strategy ?? bestSimName)\n  \u2192 emerald border + [Best \u2713] badge if true\n\nhorizonFitLabel badge:  Short-term \u2192 sky border  |  Long-term \u2192 violet border  |  other \u2192 muted\n\nCoherence label  =  coherenceLabel(coherenceScore):\n  score >= 0.72 \u2192 Strong Chain  (emerald)    score >= 0.50 \u2192 Connected    (blue)\n  score >= 0.28 \u2192 Loose         (amber)       score <  0.28 \u2192 Scattered   (muted)\nChain coherence meter bar:  h-1.5 progress bar, same color scheme\n\nMastery gain: +totalGain%   |   Final avg: finalAvg%\nTarget skills: chip badges   |   justification[] (up to 3 lines)",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "isBest: effectiveBestName === path.name  (effectiveBestName = whatIfAdvice.best_strategy ?? bestSimName)\n  \u2192 emerald border + [Best \u2713] badge if true\n\nhorizonFitLabel badge:  Short-term \u2192 sky border  |  Long-term \u2192 violet border  |  other \u2192 muted\n\nCoherence label  =  coherenceLabel(coherenceScore):\n  score >= 0.72 \u2192 Strong Chain  (emerald)    score >= 0.50 \u2192 Connected    (blue)\n  score >= 0.28 \u2192 Loose         (amber)       score <  0.28 \u2192 Scattered   (muted)\nChain coherence meter bar:  h-1.5 progress bar, same color scheme\n\nMastery gain: +totalGain%   |   Final avg: finalAvg%\nTarget skills: chip badges   |   justification[] (up to 3 lines)",
      "lineHeight": 1.4
    },
