      "updated": 1703000000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "masteryList.slice().reverse()  (asc order \u2014 low mastery first)\nEach chip: mastery color dot + name (truncated 160px) + mastery%\n\ninZPD = mastery >= 0.30 && <= 0.70  \u2192 blue border/bg chip\nactive = selected                   \u2192 primary fill\natCap = !active && count >= cap     \u2192 disabled + opacity-40\n\nonClick: toggle skillIdx in manualSkillIds[]",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "masteryList.slice().reverse()  (asc order \u2014 low mastery first)\nEach chip: mastery color dot + name (truncated 160px) + mastery%\n\ninZPD = mastery >= 0.30 && <= 0.70  \u2192 blue border/bg chip\nactive = selected                   \u2192 primary fill\natCap = !active && count >= cap     \u2192 disabled + opacity-40\n\nonClick: toggle skillIdx in manualSkillIds[]",
      "lineHeight": 1.4
    },
