      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1703000000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Payload: { mastery_vector, strategy_options:[{name,total_gain,final_avg,target_skills,coherence_score}], recommended_strategy }\nResponse: WhatIfAdvice { best_strategy, rationale, action_items[], generated_at, source: \"llm\"|\"rule_based\" }\n\nShows: [LLM-guided] or [Rule-based] badge  \u00b7  Recommended Strategy name  \u00b7  horizon hint text\nparseAdvisorRationale(text): strips **, splits lead sentence + supporting bullets + embedded action items\nadvisorActions = dedup merge of action_items[] + embeddedActions[]  \u00b7  aborted via AbortController on re-run",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Payload: { mastery_vector, strategy_options:[{name,total_gain,final_avg,target_skills,coherence_score}], recommended_strategy }\nResponse: WhatIfAdvice { best_strategy, rationale, action_items[], generated_at, source: \"llm\"|\"rule_based\" }\n\nShows: [LLM-guided] or [Rule-based] badge  \u00b7  Recommended Strategy name  \u00b7  horizon hint text\nparseAdvisorRationale(text): strips **, splits lead sentence + supporting bullets + embedded action items\nadvisorActions = dedup merge of action_items[] + embeddedActions[]  \u00b7  aborted via AbortController on re-run",
      "lineHeight": 1.4
    },
